==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Circler
<hw>Cir"cler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A mean or inferior
poet, perhaps from his habit of wandering around as a stroller; an
itinerant poet. Also, a name given to the cyclic poets. See under
<er>Cyclic</er>, <pos>a.</pos></def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>B.
Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Circlet</ent>⟦br⟧
